    • getMovieById

      public static Movie getMovieById(long id)
      Retrieves a Movie object from the list of movies based on the specified ID.

      This method iterates through the collection of Movie objects and returns the first instance whose primary key matches the provided ID. If no match is found, it returns null.

      Parameters:
      id - the primary key of the movie to be retrieved
      Returns:
      the Movie object with the specified ID, or null if no such movie exists

    • getActorById

      public static Actor getActorById(long id)
      Retrieves an Actor object from the list of actors based on the specified ID.

      This method iterates through the collection of Actor objects and returns the first instance whose primary key matches the provided ID. If no match is found, it returns null.

      Parameters:
      id - the primary key of the actor to be retrieved
      Returns:
      the Actor object with the specified ID, or null if no such actor exists
